      • states

        public static CTTraceabilityPredicate states(crafttweaker.api.block.IBlockState... allowedStates)
        Match any of the given IBlockStates.

        When called with a single parameter, it is equivalent to IBlockState as IBlockMatcher.

        参数:
        allowedStates - The list of IBlockStates to match.
        返回:
        An CTTraceabilityPredicate that returns true for any of the given blockstates.
